1 A BILL FOR AN ACT relating to the Committee on Pacific Conflict; to amend
2 section 81-836, Reissue Revised Statutes of Nebraska; to change
3 provisions relating to committee membership; to eliminate obsolete
4 provisions; to harmonize provisions; and to repeal the original
5 section.
6 Be it enacted by the people of the State of Nebraska,
